`esp_sleep_enable_timer_wakeup` is in microseconds. Reset reason after wake reports the cause.

```c
#include "esp_log.h"
#include "esp_sleep.h"

static const char *TAG = "sleep";

void app_main(void) {
    ESP_LOGI(TAG, "wake cause = %d", (int)esp_sleep_get_wakeup_cause());
    ESP_LOGI(TAG, "sleeping 30s");
    esp_sleep_enable_timer_wakeup(30ULL * 1000 * 1000);
    esp_deep_sleep_start();
}
```

